metadata.name: Transformation
metadata.description:
This guy lived usual life like all young people. But once his carefree life came to the end. He was bitten and scratched by the cheetah.

He recognizes with horror the transformation inside himself. He is looking for answers to his questions on the Internet. His life is falling apart, so now he doesn’t care his plans that he wrote down on the stickers.

Poster adds suspense. Poster woman’s look is turned to frightened  guy. Her view with a raised finger to her lips seems to say, “Shh, boy… Calm down... Keep the noise down..."

What will go ahead? What will happen with our character? This is a curse or new opportunities?
